### ğŸŸ  **HIGH #4: TrainingDetailPage â†” TrainingHubPage** (Consider Better Organization)

**Current State:**
```
TrainingHubPage (pages/TrainingHubPage.tsx) - 70 LINES
â”œâ”€ Role-based tabs (Admin only):
â”‚  â”œâ”€ My Training (all users)
â”‚  â””â”€ Admin Panel (admins only)
â”œâ”€ My Training Tab:
â”‚  â””â”€ MyTrainingTab component (training list)
â””â”€ Admin Tab:
   â””â”€ TrainingAdminTab component (manage trainings)

