â”œâ”€ Training content view
â”œâ”€ Quiz interface
â”œâ”€ Results display
â””â”€ Certificate redirect
```

**Issue:** TrainingDetailPage is reached from MyTrainingTab but exists as separate page. Navigation flow: TrainingHub â†’ MyTrainingTab â†’ TrainingDetailPage. Users must navigate through hierarchy.

**Current Flow:**
```
