â”œâ”€ MyTrainingTab (component)
â”‚  â””â”€ [Click training] â†’ Navigate to TrainingDetailPage
â””â”€ TrainingAdminTab (component)
```

**Recommendation:**
- âœ… **KEEP CURRENT STRUCTURE** - It works well
- âœ… Consider moving TrainingDetailPage content into modal/drawer (future)
- âœ… For now: Structure is clear and functional, no merge needed

**Reason:** The separation is intentional (hub for listing, detail page for content/quiz). Merging would make TrainingHubPage too complex.

