## Conclusion

**Quick Wins Available:** 2 high-impact changes (DocumentsPage deletion + AuditHubPage merge) with LOW risk and HIGH UX benefit.

**Recommended First Action:** Delete DocumentsPage and merge AuditHubPage â†” AuditLogPage. Both are straightforward and improve user experience immediately.

**Not Recommended Now:** Refactoring ProjectListPage/DetailPage structure - current design is functional and modern pattern would require significant redesign.
